 ref="#pmb41215" type="work">La martire</rs> (<rs ref="#pmb41213" type="person">Samarra</rs>)</cell><cell><rs ref="#pmb886" type="place">Mailand</rs></cell></row><row><cell><rs ref="#pmb41217" type="work">Medici</rs></cell></row></table><table><row><cell>Premiere von</cell><cell><rs ref="#pmb30445" type="work">Ennemico del popolo</rs></cell><cell><rs ref="#pmb445" type="place">Rom</rs></cell></row><row><cell><space unit="chars" quantity="5"/>“<space unit="chars" quantity="3"/>“<space unit="chars" quantity="2"/></cell><cell><rs ref="#pmb41222" type="work">Puppenfee</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><anchor xml:id="K_L00391_1" type="commentary"/><rs ref="#pmb41222" type="work">la fata del bambol</rs><note xml:id="K_L00391_1h" type="commentary">italienisch richtig: <rs ref="#pmb41222" type="work">La fata delle bambole</rs></note></cell></row></table><p>Varietés, Operetten etc. überall.</p><closer>Herzlichst Ihr <signed>Richard.</signed></closer><postscript><p>der sich auf Sie freut</p><dateline rend="right"><rs ref="#pmb595" type="place">Neapel</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date when="1894-10-23">23/X 94</date>.</dateline></postscript></div></body><back><listPerson><person xml:id="pmb10863">
